{"type": "article", "id": 13650, "title": "「 夏末单车」之发光的单车", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-18T08:03:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113540po1WUPMu8EyNcS7H.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t三年前，设计师 Eberhard Schilling 和 Antoine Capeyron 开始着手设计能够在夜里发光的自行车，他们经过三年的研发，最终推出了一款反光油漆，它们把这种特殊定制的油漆涂在自行车架上，再在表面刷上一层厚厚的清漆，可以防止锈蚀和脱落，以及意外的刮伤和磨损。此外，它们还生产了一系列反光的贴纸，<a href=\"http://happarelbicycles.berlin/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141336xUfGwvgOL0uNh93j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413361UMqrzN0DPZRBtQf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141336VwBCbT8ugQU7R5jJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141337j1KTDZW0GJNL7lXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141337NX7Rny8PgMHeADpK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}